## Common Patterns in This Project

### Adding a new page
```
app/[locale]/(storefront)/[page-name]/page.tsx
```
- Always a Server Component unless interactivity is required
- Use `generateMetadata` for SEO
- Fetch data at the page level, pass as props to components

### Adding a new component
```
components/[feature]/ComponentName.tsx
```
- Server Component default
- Add `"use client"` only for: state, effects, event handlers, browser APIs
- Use `cn()` from `lib/cn.ts` for class logic
- Use logical Tailwind properties (`ms-`, `me-`, etc.)

### Adding a translation key
1. Add the key to `messages/ar.json` with Arabic text
2. Add the same key to `messages/en.json` with English text
3. Use in component: `const t = useTranslations('namespace'); t('key')`

### New utility function
```
lib/[descriptive-name].ts
```
- Pure function — no React, no side effects unless clearly needed
- Export named functions, not default
- Type all parameters and return values
